					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2148e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2162e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1050093.dita#i1050093"
                              base="i1050093"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-23</xref>, Assignment of Claims, in solicitations and contracts expected to exceed the micro-purchase threshold, unless the contract will prohibit the assignment of claims (see <xref href="FAR-i1081480.dita#i1081480"
                              base="i1081480"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">32.803</xref>(b)). The use of the clause is not required for purchase orders. However, the clause may be used in purchase orders expected to exceed the micro-purchase threshold, that are accepted in writing by the contractor, if such use is consistent with agency policies and regulations.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2162e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If a no-setoff commitment has been authorized (see <xref href="FAR-i1081480.dita#i1081480"
                              base="i1081480"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">32.803</xref>(d)), the contracting officer shall use the clause with its AlternateI.</p>
						            </li>
